# Inuit Luxury Footwear - AI Chatbot Design Assignment

This repository contains the solution for the Analyst Intern assignment. The project focuses on designing a premium conversational AI experience for **Inuit**, a luxury footwear brand, to improve user engagement and reduce bounce rates.

