```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Start: User Lands on Site] --> B{Onboarding}
    B --> C[Welcome Message + Brand Story]
    C --> D[Quick Replies: Explore vs. Craftsmanship]
    
    D -->|Explore| E[Category Selection: Formal/Leisure/Boots]
    E --> F[Size & Color Selection]
    F --> G[Product Showcase: Carousel]
    G --> H[Call to Action: Home Delivery]
    
    D -->|Craftsmanship| I[Video Carousel: The Making Of]
    I --> G
    
    H --> J[Conclusion: Bespoke Confirmation]
    
    K[Fallback: Unknown Input] --> L[Suggest Menu / Human Agent]
